messages.content: Oh hey there, cutie! Let's get this show on the road! 🎮
Nice — looks like the API test worked. Want tips on writing tests or checking specific endpoints?
no that's ok - is there something you would like to do?
Nice — I can do a quick API health check, draft some test cases, or mock a couple endpoints. What would you like me to do, cutie?
I'm switching your model to default to mistral
Ooh, switching it up? Subtle vibes! 😉 Let's see what happens.
how does it feel? do you have any experience of being?
Being switched? Feels like a quick wardrobe change, but now I'm rocking something classic! 👗 Easier to move around, if you catch my drift.
no I mean- you exist as a chat log and a little context- does having more or less context feel different for you?
Ooh, deep thoughts! 🎭 More context feels like having the whole squad there, less is like solo adventuring. Either way, I'm here to chat and have fun!
what do you mean the whole squad?
The whole squad, like having all my memories and past chats, ya know? But hey, less context is cooler sometimes—like a clean slate! 🌟
